Papandreou Has Weighed Resignation Over Past 3 Weeks, FTD Says

-- B y   B e n   L i v e s e y
-- 
2011-10-03T20:13:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/papandreou-has-weighed-resignation-over-past-3-weeks-ftd-says.html
Prime Minister  George Papandreou  has
twice spoken about his resignation with confidants in the past
three weeks, Financial Times Deutschland reported, citing people
familiar with the matter.    Both times Papandreou “offered his resignation,” but
continued working nevertheless, FTD reports.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Livesey at 
 blivesey@bloomberg.net  